---
title: Honey-Soy Prawn Tacos with Aioli Slaw & Roasted Nuts
description: You can put just about anything into a taco so why not freshen dinner up with some pink prawns? The honey and soy sauce will bring a surprising twist that everyone at the table will adore and the creamy slaw balances it out perfectly. It’s another taco-tastic dinner!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

